  "title": "AI ENGINEER",
  "description": "<p><strong>Roles & Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Lead the design, development, and implementation of artificial intelligence (AI) and machine learning solutions to support business operations.</p></li><li><p>Manage AI-driven software projects, including planning, resource coordination, and delivery timelines.</p></li><li><p>Develop, train, test, and deploy machine learning models and data-driven applications.</p></li><li><p>Oversee data processing, data analytics, and model performance evaluation.</p></li><li><p>Collaborate with stakeholders to translate business requirements into technical AI solutions.</p></li><li><p>Ensure system security, scalability, and compliance with IT governance standards.</p></li><li><p>Supervise system integration, cloud deployment, and ongoing maintenance of AI platforms.</p></li><li><p>Provide technical guidance and leadership to development teams.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Degree in Computer Science, Artificial Intelligence, Information Technology, or related field.</p></li><li><p>Proven experience in AI, machine learning, data analytics, or software development.</p></li><li><p>Strong knowledge of programming languages such as Python, Java, or similar.</p></li><li><p>Experience with databases, cloud platforms, and system architecture.</p></li><li><p>Familiarity with project management and IT infrastructure management.</p></li><li><p>Strong analytical, leadership, and problem-solving skills.</p></li></ul>",
